com.github.naoghuman.lib.tag.core

Interface Tag

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<Tag>, Externalizable, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultTag

    public interface Tag
extends Comparable<Tag>, Externalizable
    From the basic idea a Tag is a simple String which can be used to displayed in a Button, Label or another JavaFX component.
    Tagged topics can be easily searched or analysed for a Tag.

    An instance from this Interface can be easily generated with the fluent builder TagBuilder which is the preferred way to generate an implementation from this Interface.

    Since:
    0.1.0
    Version:
    0.4.0
    Author:
    Naoghuman
    See Also:
    TagBuilder, String, Button, Label
